# Explicit install manifest. The justfile `install` recipe already lays these
# files down under debian/cosmic-utils-enroll/ during override_dh_auto_install,
# but we list them here so dh_install is a no-op safety net and the layout is
# self-documenting. Path is relative to debian/tmp by convention; here we
# install directly to debian/cosmic-utils-enroll via just, so this file is
# intentionally empty — kept so dh behaves predictably with the install
# debhelper sequence.
